data.title: Koukaku Kidoutai: Stand Alone Complex
data.meta_description: Characters, voice actors, producers and directors from the anime Koukaku Kidoutai: Stand Alone Complex (Ghost in the Shell: Stand Alone Complex) on MyAnimeList, the internet's largest anime database. In the not so distant future, mankind has advanced to a state where complete body transplants from flesh to machine is possible. This allows for great increases in both physical and cybernetic prowess and blurring the lines between the two worlds. However, criminals can also make full use of such te...
